<h2 style="margin:0 0 10px 0; font-size:22px; font-weight:600;">
    ⚠️ Payment Failed - Action Required
</h2>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:25px 0;">
    Hello {{homeBuyerName}},
</p>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    We were unable to process your recent payment. Please review the details below and try again.
</p>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    <strong>Payment Details:</strong>
</p>

<table style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0; border-collapse:collapse;">
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Reference:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;"><strong>{{paymentReference}}</strong></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Amount:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;">{{amount}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Contract:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;">{{contractNumber}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Attempted Date:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;">{{attemptDate}}</td>
    </tr>
</table>

{{#if failureReason}}
<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:15px 0;">
    <strong>Reason:</strong><br/>
    {{failureReason}}
</p>
{{/if}}

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    <strong>What to do next:</strong>
</p>
<ol style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0; padding-left:20px;">
    <li>Check that your payment details are correct</li>
    <li>Ensure sufficient funds are available</li>
    <li>Try making the payment again from your dashboard</li>
</ol>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0; color:#c0392b;">
    Please complete this payment within 7 days to avoid late fees and maintain your account in good standing.
</p>

<a href="{{dashboardLink}}"
    style="color:#ffffff; padding:8px 20px; text-decoration:none; font-size:14px; font-family:Arial, sans-serif; border-radius:12px; display:inline-block; background: linear-gradient(180deg, #049DC8 0%, #0082B5 100%); border: none; margin-top:15px;">
    Retry Payment
</a>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:20px; margin-top:30px;">
    Best, <br />
    The {{projectName}} Team.
</p>
